# cell 1
from itertools import count

import ipywidgets as W
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from bridget.display_helpers import displaydh
from IPython.display import HTML, Image, Javascript, JSON, DisplayHandle, clear_output
counter = count()

#| hide
# cell 13
w = W.Output()
display(w)
with w:
    print('cell 13.1')
    display('cell 13.2')
    display(HTML('cell 13.3'))

# cell 24
from itertools import count
from bridget.display_helpers import displaydh
from IPython.display import HTML, Javascript, clear_output
counter = count()
dh0 = displaydh(HTML('cell 24.0'), metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 24.0}})
dh1 = displaydh(
    {'application/x-notebook-state': {'feedback': True, 'watch': True, 'debug': True, 'id': next(counter)}}, 
    raw=True, metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 24.1, 'skip': True}})  # skip not needed, renderer always skipped

# cell 25
dh1.update({'application/x-notebook-state': {'id': next(counter), 'update': True}}, raw=True, 
        metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 25, 'skip': True}})

# cell 26
_ = displaydh('cell 26.1', metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 26.1, 'skip': True}})  # transient, but skip has precedence
_ = displaydh('cell 26.2', metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 26.2}})  # transient

# cell 27
_ = display('cell 27.1', metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 27.1, 'skip': True}})
_ = display('cell 27.2', metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 27.2}})

# cell 28
dh1.update({'application/x-notebook-state': {'id': next(counter), 'update': True}}, raw=True, 
        metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 28, 'skip': True}})
dh0.update(HTML('cell 28'), metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 28, 'cnt': next(counter)}})

# cell 29
dh1.update({'application/x-notebook-state': {'feedback': False, 'id': next(counter)}}, raw=True, 
        metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 29, 'skip': True}})

# cell 30
dh1.update({'application/x-notebook-state': {'watch': False, 'id': next(counter)}}, raw=True, 
        metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 30, 'skip': True}})

# cell 31
dh2 = displaydh({'application/x-notebook-state': {'feedback': True, 'watch': True, 'id': next(counter)}}, 
        raw=True, metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 31, 'skip': True}})
clear_output()

# cell 32
dh2.update({'application/x-notebook-state': {'id': next(counter)}}, raw=True, 
        metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 32, 'skip': True, 'update': True}})

# cell 36
this_id = next(counter)
_ = displaydh(metadata={'bridge': {'cell': 36, 'this': this_id}})
